    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款令人上瘾的独特塔防游戏，在网格上进行。扮演奶奶，击败一波波恶魔，拯救她的孙子孙女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292520/extras/93234d82cb0b4a2d0ec0e24fd12cd0b0.poster.avif?t=1743119988\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292520/extras/93234d82cb0b4a2d0ec0e24fd12cd0b0.webm?t=1743119988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292520/extras/93234d82cb0b4a2d0ec0e24fd12cd0b0.mp4?t=1743119988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40 个高度上瘾的关卡。</strong>关卡动态发展并具有重玩价值，因为它们永远不会重复播放。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大量强化道具。</strong>冻结时间、获得隐身、种植各种花炮塔、建造墙壁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单的控制。</strong>只需使用箭头按钮（或 wasd 键/ dpad）单手玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态游戏。</strong>不要只保卫你的门户，还要攻击他们的门户，与恶魔战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奖励策略、技能和敏捷思维。</strong>游戏中的机制确保您的胜利和快速通关取决于您的游戏方式。您不会通过磨练来解锁或升级统计数据和能力。重要的是您、您的技能以及对特定关卡中给出的内容的反应。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥创造力。</strong>通过建造墙壁和花塔来为恶魔铺设道路和陷阱，并重塑关卡以服务于您的计划。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>展示判断力。</strong>一旦门户被摧毁，关卡老板（孙子）就会诞生。您将看到他们的健康状况，并必须决定何时建造足够的防御来击败他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>实现最佳时间。</strong>尝试在每个关卡上实现更好的时间，奖励您在更深层次上掌握游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292520/extras/60932395721c07c7408102efd713a2fe.poster.avif?t=1743119988\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292520/extras/60932395721c07c7408102efd713a2fe.webm?t=1743119988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292520/extras/60932395721c07c7408102efd713a2fe.mp4?t=1743119988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
